然話GPS可能唔準確<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n左去西隧口你都唔知？<br />\n將軍澳返屯門正常都行龍翔道返啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢一黎就上左觀塘繞道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我拍醒我隔離個個 佢話可能龍翔道塞車<br />\n講完佢又訓返<br />\n咁我又唔知頭唔知路 見到奧海城先知出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW個程收多左我幾十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔好話，行老龍同行機隧加士居道其實係爭一公里左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過有客同我講行機隧條路仲舒服過行老龍，多都只係十元八塊不過唔駛老龍身心震"},{"pid":"7ad12cf408dd1c6764967a1b0cc00099acefc7b2","tid":134120,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T17:40:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52b7e60debbec0d45830ed4d8f912aa65982937d","tid":134120,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:17:29.000Z","msg":"惡性循環黎<br />\n個價太咸，司機等有加成先接<br />\n到有加成，就變成個客唔想搭，等冇加成先叫車<br />\n要拆掂佢唯有叫uber抽少啲水，或者酌量加下最低消費<br />\n當然真正最有效係將網絡叫車規範化合法左佢，到時有競爭uber就唔會越做越頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5db1ea6bbb25386ce13ad08cf25f1bde1d5244","tid":134120,"uid":60967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:21:21.000Z","msg":"睇佢點分帳就知間公司幾仆街<br />\n最近重爆出係google到偷技術"},{"pid":"bf789f155bebbcbc0df50297b8385ea2293fe87e","tid":134120,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:33:05.000Z","msg":"根據華人的劣根性<br />\n華人唔會做得好架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ef64574d1342afd77345ad623652e1a32aa52c","tid":134120,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T18:37:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根據華人的劣根性<br />\n華人唔會做得好架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockqu