eb8879664e45d18b8eaf2f11004b2","tid":134120,"uid":16937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:00:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>放工時間九龍過海，打黎叫我cut 單，我係咪可以投訴</blockquote><br />\n打俾你cut 咪好<br />\n有d 仆街等10min 唔郁等你cut<br />\n你唔接就單聲丫</blockquote><br />\n其實Suppose司機唔可以問乘客去邊，只可以問邊到上車<br />\n司機係等乘客上左車start 個下先知<br />\n所以其實可以直接唔答佢去邊</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 通常唔答司機都無你咁好氣 一野即cut"},{"pid":"b07a4728ff749b5182cc21f01f02831ede73e3e7","tid":134120,"uid":24218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有d morning 車。<br />\n上次去機場，你去機場都一箱二箱<br />\n果期岩岩出morning<br />\n見到架morning 呆撚左<br />\n後面放三個行李，另加一個放大脾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多行李CALL 7人先肯定放得落而可以坐得鬆動<br />\nCALL X 如果唔係黎架細7應該都係咁上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你啦<br />\n又要平又要人地架車大<br />\n唔撚識call black車嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n使唔使人哋俾埋個屎忽你隊呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1069943f3f3b785e857444a78c016608304853f","tid":134120,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T10:41:41.000Z","msg":"貴過的士已經唔會搭<br />\n<br />\ncall有折的士, 司機好人得多"},{"pid":"ae73ae2f5b6e0af44a106ec83a1d4ad96297cc29","tid":134120,"uid":53220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T11:12:43.000Z","msg":"以前加乘都有得睇 而加冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae155fda759dd6ee6ddb03fae166cb504f180af","tid":134120,"uid":734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我尋晚青衣去九龍灣，佢唔識路都算<br />\n佢本身都冇乜野，去到佢叫我俾5星佢<br />\n我都冇所謂話好啦，點知佢唔開車門要睇到我俾左5星同評語先開車門<br />\n痴撚線，我本身都覺得ok預左落左車就俾，但佢咁迫我真係好撚嬲<br />\n有冇咩方法可以投訴佢</blockquote><br />\n打電話叫猶太人嚟捉載客取酬咪得囉，即刻開門俾你啦</blockquote><br />\n好似有得直接report</blockquote><br />\n直接report 唔會有得立即落車</blockquote><br />\n我今日睇返原來可以改返個rating，我已經report左佢<br />\n條氣真係唔順，本身我都諗住俾，我不嬲都落車就俾<br />\n但而家佢咁迫我俾就勁唔順"},{"pid":"dd75d8f02d917a0244b3585c29acb5c89a1a0342","tid":134120,"uid":28258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:17:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有d morning 車。<br />\n上次去機場，你去機場都一箱二箱<br />\n果期岩岩出morning<br />\n見到架morning 呆撚左<br />\n後面放三個行李，另加一個放大脾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解唔call gogovan?"},{"pid":"08d0406247322a0a823f475ab809c53cfb8bd757","tid":134120,"uid":45958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T18:18:52.000Z","msg":"笑鳩左...成班係到鳩吹...睇完真係笑到仆街<br />\n上車至講目的地？<br />\n你冇坐過就吾好出聲啦...沖出黎戴頭盔"},{"pid":"8828f5290e5a5bedcf4c210e320ee4604e2ad3f7","tid":134120,"uid":16362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T22:33:33.000Z","msg":"而家一口價，司機一定係揀最短條路，無得兜"},{"pid":"657765f89bb5d9e843f9904f658eefcb4a1ee6ae","tid":134120,"uid":81664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T23:27:39.000Z","msg":"而家點解仲貴過的士<br />\n上次沙田番元朗諗住call uber, 點知一望價錢要$240<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8折的都平過佢"},{"pid":"501bea59e332e07a2dfa4830dd171bb5c2143c65","tid":134120,"uid":11891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T23:37:04.000Z","msg":"uber 成撚日唔識路 上次去大學站 屌佢 入撚咗中大再出返科學園去大學站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a40d7806de74f702675bf8003df14f7788bb1f5","tid":134120,"uid":17167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T23:53:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>笑鳩左...成班係到鳩吹...睇完真係笑到仆街<br />\n上車至講目的地？<br />\n你冇坐過就吾好出聲啦...沖出黎戴頭盔</blockquote><br />\n無講錯啊，司機係要你上左車先知你去邊架喎"},{"pid":"486012ccd5ea791fafd312701644c3ad4b375f11","tid":13412